</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-275_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-276_"><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-277_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-278_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-279_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_44d5e43d-d8c9-44c3-9613-101860fffeae.png?v=1708705767" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_44d5e43d-d8c9-44c3-9613-101860fffeae.png?v=1708705767 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_44d5e43d-d8c9-44c3-9613-101860fffeae_1500x.png?v=1708705767 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_44d5e43d-d8c9-44c3-9613-101860fffeae_1000x.png?v=1708705767 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_44d5e43d-d8c9-44c3-9613-101860fffeae_500x.png?v=1708705767 320w" width="1766" height="1179" alt="3.png__PID:b0d3618e-fba4-4a0f-a79f-c40a5778b6ee" title="Mastering Strategic Decision-Making with Advanced BI Tools: BI Implementation Challenges and Solutions - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-281_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-282_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-284_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The sheer scale and impact of the NHS underscore the significance of clinical governance:
</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-286_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-287_ pf-text-1">The Department of Health and Social Care boasts one of the largest departmental budgets in the UK, with funding exceeding £180 billion, highlighting the vast resources dedicated to healthcare.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-289_ pf-text-1">The NHS ranks as one of the world's largest employers, comparable only to global giants such as the Indian Ministry of Defence and the US Department of Defense, emphasising its massive operational scale.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-291_ pf-text-1">Daily patient interactions with NHS services numbered approximately 1.6 million in 2021/22, reflecting the extensive reach and critical role of the NHS in public health.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-293_ pf-text-1">Comparative analyses internationally acclaim the NHS as one of the top-performing and most cost-effective healthcare systems globally, showcasing its efficiency and quality.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-295_ pf-text-1">The establishment of 42 integrated care systems (ICSs) across the country signifies a tailored approach to healthcare, acknowledging the diverse health needs and metrics of different populations.
</li></ul><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-297_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This backdrop of robust funding, vast employment, and extensive service delivery paints a clear picture of the NHS's pivotal role in healthcare, reinforcing the necessity of effective clinical governance in sustaining service quality and safety.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-299_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-300_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-301_ pf-heading-1-h3">Defining clinical governance
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_fad5728a-4a08-4d32-9263-b0dbad7576ce.png?v=1708704365" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_fad5728a-4a08-4d32-9263-b0dbad7576ce.png?v=1708704365 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_fad5728a-4a08-4d32-9263-b0dbad7576ce_1000x.png?v=1708704365 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/4_fad5728a-4a08-4d32-9263-b0dbad7576ce_500x.png?v=1708704365 320w" width="1308" height="872" alt="4.png__PID:f4f772d4-442e-40d3-a18e-fba45a0f279f" title="Boosting Operational Efficiency: How BI Transforms Businesses Beyond Analytics: The Strategic Value of BI - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-303_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-304_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by halfpoint

